# BIFROST — Distributed AI Inference Platform

Intelligent routing of coding and knowledge work across heterogeneous hardware.
85-92% cost savings versus cloud-only approaches.

## Architecture

- **Bifrost** — Primary workstation (RX 9070 XT, Tier 1a)
- **Hearth** — Always-on server (embeddings, monitoring, GitOps)
- **Forge** — Portable AI workstation (96GB VRAM, Tiers 1b/2/2.5)

## Modes

| Mode | Description |
|------|------------|
| JARVIS | Full power — all machines |
| WORKSHOP | Bifrost + Hearth only |
| WORKSHOP-OFFLINE | Privacy-first, zero cloud |

See `docs/MASTER-PLAN.md` for the complete architecture.

## Structure

`
k8s/              Kubernetes manifests (FluxCD managed)
flux/              FluxCD sync configuration
control-plane/     Observer, Broadcaster, Arbiter, Router
scripts/           Per-machine setup and maintenance
dashboards/        Grafana JSON exports
docs/              Architecture documentation
`
